6:
I'm done... So tired of... trying to
make it here...
7:
I wanna go home... Mom... Dad... I
miss you...
9: What the hell? Hey! Are you okay?!
14: What in the world is going on?!
18:
All the people who awakened to
their powers are resonating... and
rewriting reality? But that...
22:
This is exactly like what happened
back then... But how do we stop it?!
28:
Is this world going to start melting
away too?!
32:
Doubtful. As far as I can see, it's only
the awakened ones slipping away.
35:
Their fervent desire to return home
will remain unfulfilled, because
unfortunately for them, Palpebra
exists outside the Void.
38:
Instead, they will vanish into a
dream of their own making, turning
away from this reality that they were
forced into.
41: We'll go home... Back to Japan...
44:
Why is this happening though? They
were all normal until a second ago!
48:
They were hiding their fears this
whole time... Forcing themselves to
focus on the future...
56:
First things first, we have to take that
thing down! Liam!
61: Then... that's it. They're all doomed.
73:
Can you hear me, everyone? It's me,
Luciada, Voluntas' student council
president!
79:
I know a lot of you don't see me in a
favorable light, but please, listen to
me for the time being!
83:
You need to call out to the people of
Shibuya! Even if they don't respond,
keep at it! Now follow my lead!
87:
You belong here! You have a place
here!
90:
And you aren't alone! We're with you,
all the way! So don't you dare
disappear on us!
94:
Y-yeah, come back to us, you hear?
We're with you too! All of us!
105:
Because I ordered it, of course!
Ohohoho!
109:
You said this song was a source of
comfort for the Shibuyans, yes?
Then it shall surely bring them back
to their senses!
120: We can't forget the vocals, too!
124:
I'll make sure Binary Planet reaches
their hearts!
129: Everything will be fine. Trust us.
133:
All right. I'll get the relay system
working as best as I can!
138:
...Your song may have gone places
you didn't know about.
141:
But it didn't leave you behind—it's
taking you somewhere new. So what
do you say? Want to sing it together?
149:
Your song has the power to bring
people together. I promise it does.
154:
If... you need a keyboardist, then I
can do that much!
158:
Sounds good to me! Let's do this,
Hibiki!
163:
I'll run protection duty while you
perform. They won't touch a hair on
you.
168: Leave the ugly critter to us!
180:
A serpent is quite the formidable
foe...
185:
I assume you have a plan. You're
good at making those, aren't you?
189:
...I have a forbidden incantation that
might prove useful, but it requires
draining someone's life force to use.
193:
Oh, is that all? Then use mine and
finish the beast off!
198:
...Very well. If you're resolved, then so
am I.
201:
O darkness from whence we came...
and where we shall return...
210:
Haha, you can handle quite a lot,
can't you? I won't hold back.
214:
Take form and become my blade!
Venitas Gladius!
229:
...The way forward starts with one
step.
241:
Please listen to our rendition of
Binary Planet!
247:
No moshing allowed for today's
concert, bud!
251:
Nobody's getting near that stage on
our watch!
